h/auth.service.ts` - Stub service with register (age check) and login (returns s
tub tokens)\n6. `apps/api/src/modules/auth/auth.module.ts` - Basic module\n7. `a
pps/api/src/modules/auth/dto/register.dto.ts` - Empty DTO with no class-validato
